reviewText: My kids enjoy The little Car a lot! Super cute!
This is great for small children, all boys who like  cars would enjoy this series!
Kids love it: mistery and adventure!

The absolutely the worst kid's video ever.  It is highly inappropriate for children.  Insulting language and adult themes.  Yet the animation is so bad, anyone over age 3 wouldn't care to watch it.  The disc is best used as a Frisbee.
